8f54014a-12d5-4d12-8f05-acbe4fedf909.title: Nature Spirit
8f54014a-12d5-4d12-8f05-acbe4fedf909.text:
Well, hello there again, I was just enjoying the grotto.
Many thanks for your help, I couldn't have become a
Spirit of nature without you.

9e1b9716-742a-452a-8b96-07b5d0c119f0.title: Nature Spirit
9e1b9716-742a-452a-8b96-07b5d0c119f0.text:
I must complete the transformation now. Just stand
there and watch the show, apparently it's quite good!

09186c62-5862-4481-8548-72d6f97e4097.title: Nature Spirit
09186c62-5862-4481-8548-72d6f97e4097.text:
Hmmm, good, the transformation is complete. Now, my
friend, in return for your assistance, I will help you to
kill the Ghasts. First bring to me a silver sickle so that I
can bless it for you.

814f21d3-353f-421f-adb8-a086c6353a1c.title: Nature Spirit
814f21d3-353f-421f-adb8-a086c6353a1c.text:
The sickle is the symbol and weapon of the Druid, you
need to construct one of silver so that I can bless it,
with its powers you will be able to defeat the Ghasts of
Mort Myre.

options.text: Where would I get a silver sickle?
What will you do to the silver sickle?
How can a blessed sickle help me to defeat the Ghasts?

bec7fb1e-02b5-4433-a613-26cead4ae6c0.title: <player>
bec7fb1e-02b5-4433-a613-26cead4ae6c0.text: Where would I get a silver sickle?

7b2b4947-c112-4d3a-b2a8-b1bbf9c5a273.title: Nature Spirit
7b2b4947-c112-4d3a-b2a8-b1bbf9c5a273.text:
You could make one yourself if you're artisan enough.
I've heard of a distant sandy place where you can buy
the mould that you require, it's similar in many respects
to the creating of a holy symbol.

c589f5fb-bdc6-4386-9723-ea71a6dc72fc.title: <player>
c589f5fb-bdc6-4386-9723-ea71a6dc72fc.text: What will you do to the silver sickle?

d0476816-9e42-4f05-a7cc-b1e43236755a.title: Nature Spirit
d0476816-9e42-4f05-a7cc-b1e43236755a.text:
Why, I will give it my blessings so that the very swamp
in which you stand will blossom and bloom!

81b7f173-70da-425e-8451-47d92ce9be1c.title: <player>
81b7f173-70da-425e-8451-47d92ce9be1c.text: How can a blessed sickle help me to defeat the Ghasts?

d343a003-46e8-42fb-a08f-80e3924bc9b1.title: Nature Spirit
d343a003-46e8-42fb-a08f-80e3924bc9b1.text:
My blessings will entice nature to bloom in Mort Myre!
And then with natures harvest you can fill a druids
pouch and release the Ghasts from their torment.

3d325fa6-8e94-4d47-bfe0-86a991a85955.title: Nature Spirit
3d325fa6-8e94-4d47-bfe0-86a991a85955.text: Have you brought me the silver sickle?

dcaba613-64fc-4bfc-980d-1e48ff55bb2b.title: <player>
dcaba613-64fc-4bfc-980d-1e48ff55bb2b.text: Yes, here it is. What are you going to do with it?

55eccade-ec7e-433f-92e6-eb6c0805a844.title: Nature Spirit
55eccade-ec7e-433f-92e6-eb6c0805a844.text:
My friend, I will bless it for you and you will then be
able to accomplish great things. Now then, I must cast
the enchantment. You can bless a new sickle by dipping
it in the holy water of the grotto.

3f3d2557-d4df-41ec-b9ec-09bf57ad14f7.text:
Your sickle has been blessed!  If you lose the blessed
sickle, you can bless a new sickle by dipping it in
the grotto waters. ~

d733ab41-7978-4060-8edc-ba7a869d2f23.title: Nature Spirit
d733ab41-7978-4060-8edc-ba7a869d2f23.text:
Now you can go forth and make the swamp bloom.
Collect natures bounty to fill a druids pouch. So armed
will the Ghasts be bound to you until, you flee or they
are defeated.

6ab7fda4-ee84-4051-84b3-94c28377bb58.title: Nature Spirit
6ab7fda4-ee84-4051-84b3-94c28377bb58.text:
Before I can make this grotto into an Altar of Nature,
I need to be sure that the Ghasts will be kept at bay.
Go forth into Mort Myre and slay three Ghasts. You'll
be releasing their souls from Mort Myre.

060819a7-8989-4cbd-8aca-f309d4f3fa82.text: The nature spirit gives you an empty pouch.

0a8e2c68-aaaa-4256-a6e0-54725ba2bd86.title: Nature Spirit
0a8e2c68-aaaa-4256-a6e0-54725ba2bd86.text:
You'll need this in order to collect together natures
bounty. When it contains items, it will bind the Ghast to
you until you flee or it is defeated.

499a4292-41bc-4256-9c5c-5198700f3bc0.title: Nature Spirit
499a4292-41bc-4256-9c5c-5198700f3bc0.text: Have you brought me the silver sickle?

fb620fd1-22f7-4f77-bac6-fcf939218983.title: Nature Spirit
fb620fd1-22f7-4f77-bac6-fcf939218983.text: Well, come to me when you have it.

cf19f0fa-02cd-4ce4-9b70-6725ce6d2cb6.title: Nature Spirit
cf19f0fa-02cd-4ce4-9b70-6725ce6d2cb6.text:
Hello again my friend, have you defeated three Ghasts
as I asked you?

872ada4c-58cd-4f81-8720-86feec558840.title: <player>
872ada4c-58cd-4f81-8720-86feec558840.text:
Yes, I've killed all three and their spirits have been
released!

7fa799b2-afc7-4b3b-bf43-abb6d3fab22b.title: Nature Spirit
7fa799b2-afc7-4b3b-bf43-abb6d3fab22b.text:
Many thanks my friend, you have completed your
quest! I can now change this place into a holy
sanctuary! And forever will it now be an Altar of
Nature!

a3b83502-7f39-47d9-87e7-bd9a49c5bb42.title: Nature Spirit
a3b83502-7f39-47d9-87e7-bd9a49c5bb42.text:
Hello again my friend, have you defeated three Ghasts
as I asked you?

19f73454-9606-4344-96b1-7d7f8cb86492.title: Nature Spirit
19f73454-9606-4344-96b1-7d7f8cb86492.text:
Well, when you do, please come to me and I'll reward
you!

options.text: How do I get to attack the Ghasts?
What can I do with this sickle?

afff3746-0c43-470e-8312-a6a74afdf541.title: <player>
afff3746-0c43-470e-8312-a6a74afdf541.text: How do I get to attack the Ghasts?

99fc7b2b-5b45-414d-8800-0fce14b30e1d.title: Nature Spirit
99fc7b2b-5b45-414d-8800-0fce14b30e1d.text:
Go forth and with the sickle make the swamp bloom.
Collect natures bounty to fill a druids pouch. So armed
will the Ghasts be bound to you until, you flee or they
are defeated.

d7f93b3c-2f9c-479a-bfca-0506994754e5.title: Nature Spirit
d7f93b3c-2f9c-479a-bfca-0506994754e5.text:
It is for collecting natures bounty, once it contains the
blossomed items of the swamp, it will make the Ghasts
appear and you can then attack them.

1e07daaf-5fa8-4111-a729-c84e089584ce.title: <player>
1e07daaf-5fa8-4111-a729-c84e089584ce.text: What can I do with this sickle?

f42d9b34-8d7b-42aa-9a16-5550a7996890.title: Nature Spirit
f42d9b34-8d7b-42aa-9a16-5550a7996890.text:
You may use it wisely within the area of Mort Myre to
affect natures balance and bring forth a bounty of
natures harvest. Once collected into the druid pouch will
the Ghast be apparent.

f6cd2db8-742d-432f-934c-39ce4a723b19.title: Nature Spirit
f6cd2db8-742d-432f-934c-39ce4a723b19.text:
If you should lose the blessed sickle, simply bring
another to my altar of nature and refresh it in the
grotto waters.

4677b0aa-caff-4635-9b77-e8222f8d5358.title: Nature Spirit
4677b0aa-caff-4635-9b77-e8222f8d5358.text:
Welcome to my Altar to Nature! Farewell my friend,
and keep those Ghasts at bay!
